Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.61,0:00:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:06.15,0:00:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Am I the first one here today?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No way.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:21.04,0:00:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, morning, Ayane{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.50,0:00:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.21,0:00:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,How could she?!
Dialogue: 10,0:01:59.14,0:02:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,To my friends at the Foreclosure Task Force:
Dialogue: 10,0:02:02.64,0:02:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,For starters, sorry for saying goodbye via letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.73,0:02:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For starters, sorry for saying goodbye via letter.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:08.73,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When you're my age,\nyou prefer the more old-fashioned ways.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:13.24,0:02:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've actually been receiving offers for a while.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:18.16,0:02:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}They want me to work as a mercenary for Kaiser PMC.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.50,0:02:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In exchange, they promised to pay\nover half the debt Abydos owes Kaiser.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:26.83,0:02:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's the gist of it.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:29.09,0:02:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I may not look like it,\nbut I've actually got a bit of a reputation.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:34.18,0:02:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know I got all preachy back at the Black Market,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.51,0:02:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and I'm sorry for going back on my own words.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.81,0:02:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But this should at least give\nthe Task Force some breathing room.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:48.86,0:02:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have to do this.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:53.11,0:02:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As the final member of the student council,\nthis is my responsibility to bear.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.28,0:02:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So this is goodbye.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.00,0:03:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,To {*}our teacher{*Sensei}:
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.79,0:03:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know it's not exactly a secret,\nbut I used to hate adults.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day Shiroko{**-chan} brought you to our clubroom,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:14.42,0:03:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I immediately assumed you were\njust another good-for-nothing adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.76,0:03:24.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But you were quick to prove me wrong.\nYou're part of the team now. {uh i don't love the part of the team part but its already out so wtv -rapid}{### we can look at other options for batch}
Dialogue: 10,0:03:25.60,0:03:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So I'm leaving them in your care, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.69,0:03:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're their teacher. They trust you.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:32.28,0:03:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sure they'll be fine.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.32,0:03:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad I got to meet an adult like you before I...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.78,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nah, that's more than enough sappy stuff for one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:44.37,0:03:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:45.62,0:03:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nonomi{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.96,0:03:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:48.25,0:03:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.04,0:03:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do this for me.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Protect our school.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.84,0:03:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sure, it may be covered in sand and dust,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.30,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but it's all I have left.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:02.31,0:04:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And one last thing.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.43,0:04:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We may end up having to fight\neach other as enemies one day.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:09.06,0:04:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The day that happens,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.61,0:04:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want you to destroy my halo.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:14.23,0:04:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:16.86,0:04:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.28,0:04:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She literally {\i1}just{\i0} told us people\ndo crazy things when they're desperate!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.78,0:04:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Does she think we'll accept this?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:26.50,0:04:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.66,0:04:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go find her.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.96,0:04:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to help her!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:30.79,0:04:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down, Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.29,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,She's right! We need to assess the situation first.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:36.09,0:04:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But Hoshino{**-senpai}'s—
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.31,0:04:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep firing until the area's secure!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.06,0:04:53.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Abydos student council's\nlast remaining member has quit.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The time has come.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.69,0:04:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We, the Kaiser Corporation,\nwill seize control of Abydos High School!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.36,0:05:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Several hundred Kaiser PMC troops on approach!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.41,0:05:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,We have reports of shots fired in the city!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.04,0:05:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why now of all times?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:08.25,0:05:10.12,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to engage.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:10.12,0:05:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But what about Hoshino{**-senpai}?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, stay calm.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:13.67,0:05:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Evacuating civilians takes top priority.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.10,0:05:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could they...
Dialogue: 10,0:05:26.35,0:05:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm hanging in there.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:29.31,0:05:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:31.73,0:05:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not sure, either.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:35.82,0:05:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Foreclosure Task Force spotted! Over here!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:38.69,0:05:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:41.65,0:05:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to someplace safe for now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.95,0:05:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.29,0:05:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-senpai}!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:54.79,0:05:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you now!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.30,0:05:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, get a grip!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.30,0:06:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You get that side!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:05.64,0:06:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.72,0:06:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! These girls are tough!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.35,0:06:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Nonomi!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:12.06,0:06:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.95,0:06:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:25.24,0:06:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm all right.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.54,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They just keep coming.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.29,0:06:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to hold the line.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.22,0:06:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I originally intended to face you at the school.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:46.89,0:06:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But I appreciate you meeting me halfway,\nstudents of Abydos High School.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.47,0:06:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just attacking the city at this point!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.39,0:06:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter if you own the land here.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing gives you the right to do that!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, the school still belongs to Abydos!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:02.65,0:07:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of invasion is a clear violation of the law!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:05.28,0:07:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll report you to the GSC!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.32,0:07:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You scumbags!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:09.87,0:07:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Give Hoshino{**-senpai} back!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.95,0:07:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, spare me the childish fantasies.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:15.21,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You think reporting me will do anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:17.88,0:07:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Interesting little theory.\nWhy don't you test it out right now?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.46,0:07:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've already begged them for help\ncountless times before, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:26.30,0:07:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did it ever amount to anything?\nDid they ever lift a finger to help you?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:32.01,0:07:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you finally understand?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.31,0:07:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Struggle all you want. Nothing will change.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:39.19,0:07:44.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And now Takanashi Hoshino, the last vestige\nof the student council, has dropped out.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:44.69,0:07:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Abydos no longer has a student council.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.03,0:07:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,And you are no longer anybody at all.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:52.83,0:07:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Student council or no,\nAbydos still has the Task Force!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:58.17,0:08:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not gonna let you get away with th—
Dialogue: 10,0:08:00.46,0:08:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,The Task Force isn't an\nofficially sanctioned organisation.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:04.51,0:08:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.42,0:08:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.34,0:08:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time we formed the Task Force,\nthe student council was already defunct{/gone}.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.18,0:08:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:12.93,0:08:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.10,0:08:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're merely a phantom club.\nNo documentation, no official approval.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.23,0:08:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You have nothing that proves you exist!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.28,0:08:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But here's the good news.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:25.86,0:08:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Once Abydos High is no more,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.36,0:08:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll finally be free of that debt for good!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:33.16,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.03,0:08:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,But if that happens, what about\nall the hard work we've put in so far?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:37.37,0:08:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.62,0:08:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you {\i1}really{\i0} planning on paying back your debt\nover the next couple hundred years?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:44.13,0:08:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.84,0:08:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And here I thought you were simply waiting for\na convenient excuse to end this charade.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.35,0:08:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why {\i1}did{\i0} you all work so hard, then?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it all for?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:58.39,0:09:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you... If you say one more word...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:01.23,0:09:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll shoot.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Will fighting here change anything?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.94,0:09:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.49,0:09:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we stop them here,\nwhat happens afterwards?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.99,0:09:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if we somehow took back our school,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.75,0:09:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,we still have a huge debt looming over us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:23.58,0:09:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,The land we lost won't magically come back.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:26.80,0:09:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,And above all, Hoshino{**-senpai}\nand the student council are gone.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.22,0:09:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at us.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.80,0:09:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,We're nothing but a phantom club.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.14,0:09:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What other option do we have?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.81,0:09:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Ayane{**-chan}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:43.52,0:09:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:44.81,0:09:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why us and nobody else?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.73,0:09:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:49.15,0:09:51.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we supposed to do?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:55.37,0:09:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A large explosion reported north of here!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.33,0:10:00.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Bravo Platoon got caught in the blast!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:00.91,0:10:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? {NANI}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.66,0:10:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosions to the east, too!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.62,0:10:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Mike Platoon got hit by a massive explosion—
Dialogue: 10,0:10:08.46,0:10:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.67,0:10:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.09,0:10:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd rather die than listen to\nyour pathetic wailing for a moment longer.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.35,0:10:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"An eye for an eye."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:18.56,0:10:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"A tooth for a tooth."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:20.02,0:10:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"We tread a path none may follow,\nand do so without mercy."
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.86,0:10:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't that your motto, Masked Swimsuit Gang?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.95,0:10:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:38.08,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't fall for a bunch of pushovers.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:41.41,0:10:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Chillax, Aru{**-chan}. {## I WILL DIE ON THIS HILL}{Then perish. --ik}{based -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.91,0:10:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,They get the message.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.08,0:10:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Girls with glasses are quite delicate.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.46,0:10:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,They can't help but crack under pressure.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:49.30,0:10:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you doing here?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:51.96,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But y'know what?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:53.34,0:10:56.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You make a girl with glasses cry,\nand there'll be hell to pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:56.76,0:10:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,So you asked for this.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:59.18,0:11:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna paint the town red with your guts!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:01.64,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's Problem Solver 68!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:05.19,0:11:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to tell right from left, wrong from right.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.11,0:11:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Every path you take leads to failure.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.94,0:11:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And even once you stumble down the right one,\nall that awaits you is another dark tunnel.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Backup is here!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.58,0:11:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.42,0:11:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Your friend's in danger, isn't she?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:35.13,0:11:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you just gonna sit there feeling sorry\nwhile they take everything from you?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.30,0:11:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to take this lying down?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you telling me you're such pathetic cowards?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:47.85,0:11:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Problem Solver!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:49.86,0:11:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're nothing but lowly dogs!\nHow dare you turn on me?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.73,0:11:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, put a lid on it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I much prefer working with these girls.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.78,0:11:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all there is to it.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:59.74,0:12:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only natural for a villain to stab\ntheir employer in the back, no?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.87,0:12:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 10,0:12:05.20,0:12:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.41,0:12:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Spoken like a true villain.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.83,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the pep talk we needed.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to doubt ourselves!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.50,0:12:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Who cares if our club is unofficial?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.51,0:12:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got bigger things to worry about!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:19.72,0:12:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We {\i1}will{\i0} save Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else is secondary.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.39,0:12:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You still want to waste your time\nwith this pointless resistance?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.48,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare you—
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.39,0:12:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,No! How dare {\i1}you{\i0} torment my precious student?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:31.69,0:12:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be taking Hoshino back!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.78,0:12:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't screw with me!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:36.07,0:12:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You think you can just get on your soapbox\nand start making demands?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine then, I have just the thing for you!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.04,0:12:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But sir, it's still a prototype!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.71,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too dangerous to deploy!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.29,0:12:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Silence!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:54.42,0:12:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I will teach them what it means to defy me!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.26,0:13:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.10,0:13:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This exosuit is the pinnacle of\nour company's technology!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:11.23,0:13:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Its armaments and armour are crafted\nfrom the finest materials.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the cutting edge of weaponry!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.57,0:13:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow! It's so big!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.49,0:13:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-What do we do?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:23.91,0:13:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This could get messy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.29,0:13:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,True, this won't be easy.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.25,0:13:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's only if it's us four.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:36.13,0:13:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Back us up.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:40.88,0:13:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:41.80,0:13:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:43.26,0:13:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Alley-oop!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.85,0:13:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a dent.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:52.98,0:13:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's pointless!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.36,0:13:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just cheating!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.28,0:14:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't want to be caught\non the business end of those.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.95,0:14:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It should have some kind of weakness.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:07.49,0:14:08.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Explosives.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.79,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,How many explosives do you have left?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:12.04,0:14:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm down if you have a plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.63,0:14:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:15.88,0:14:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.34,0:14:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I don't care how bad the odds are.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.97,0:14:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how outlaws are!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:25.89,0:14:28.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your time!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.89,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.81,0:14:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our cue!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.39,0:14:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:42.40,0:14:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You thought you could flank us that easily?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:44.74,0:14:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in the way. Move, please!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:50.62,0:14:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:51.75,0:14:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, um...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:53.75,0:14:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, eyes forward! Let's go!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:56.50,0:14:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit! Don't let them through!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:59.84,0:15:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.88,0:15:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What do we do? We can't just destroy the store.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:08.22,0:15:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a grenade?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:09.97,0:15:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! But watch this!
