Dialogue: 10,0:15:18.56,0:15:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! That's a neat little trick!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:21.23,0:15:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:22.86,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll wrap things up here.{heh -p}
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.24,0:15:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.66,0:15:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Break a leg!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When will you learn that resistance is futile?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little longer...
Dialogue: 10,0:15:42.05,0:15:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're plotting,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:44.92,0:15:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I've had about enough of your little games.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:54.02,0:15:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's where you were hiding!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:56.23,0:15:57.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Serika{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:57.10,0:15:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.85,0:16:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you! Hold still!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:09.57,0:16:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be dangerous.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.37,0:16:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't keep hiding behind others.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:22.67,0:16:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick his ass.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:23.84,0:16:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:26.30,0:16:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got your back!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.51,0:16:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you pay.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.60,0:16:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you little...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.31,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like they've started.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:43.98,0:16:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.61,0:16:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take care of our part, Haruka{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:48.36,0:16:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, let's.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:54.08,0:16:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like Mutsuki and Haruka can handle it.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:01.50,0:17:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Nice try.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.92,0:17:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're set on getting in the way.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.96,0:17:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You're ruining the atmosphere.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:09.59,0:17:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind cutting that out?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.76,0:17:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You filthy rats!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Scurrying around in the dirt!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.43,0:17:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have just stayed buried underneath the sand!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:27.40,0:17:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a thorn in my side!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.92,0:17:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You call this cutting edge?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:54.14,0:17:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You little shit!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.60,0:17:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you really think you had me cornered?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:58.10,0:18:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Your puny little body means nothing!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.60,0:18:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Just try and stop the 12,860 horsepower of this craft!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:09.61,0:18:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(-500,0,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}What the—
Dialogue: 10,0:18:14.49,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And boom goes the dynamite!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:16.58,0:18:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.16,0:18:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:29.09,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got guts, standing your ground\nin the face of all this firepower.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:34.93,0:18:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Save it for someone who cares.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:37.39,0:18:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if only you had the brains to match.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.64,0:18:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Like that Hoshino girl, or whatever her name was.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.77,0:18:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just give up already?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:47.11,0:18:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.94,0:18:51.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko! Five meters behind you!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're looking?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.20,0:19:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.67,0:19:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Teacher{*Sensei}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:11.38,0:19:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:20.26,0:19:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hoshino{**-senpai}...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.89,0:19:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not easy up front, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:31.44,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What? How?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:33.36,0:19:36.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\t(1.2,\3c&HFFFFFF&\4c&HFFFFFF&)}Th-This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:44.58,0:19:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiroko{**-chan}!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:47.12,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. No problem.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:49.71,0:19:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness it worked.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:52.05,0:19:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Ayane.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.01,0:19:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And Nonomi and Serika, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.59,0:19:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All according to plan.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:59.30,0:20:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were cutting it a bit close there.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:01.76,0:20:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I figured if anyone\ncould pull it off, it'd be them.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Chairman! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get you treated!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.69,0:20:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,About time {\i1}you{\i0} gave up, don't you think?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:15.15,0:20:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not done yet!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\alpha&HFF&\blur10}What? You really want to keep goi{\1a&H00&\3a&H50&}ng?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:16.82,0:20:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You really want to keep going?
Dialogue: 9,0:20:20.12,0:20:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}Honestly, I wouldn't mind going {\alpha&HFF&}for round two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.12,0:20:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I wouldn't mind going for round two.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.66,0:20:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We're falling back. For now.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:25.50,0:20:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Regroup our forces!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.54,0:20:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yessir!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall back!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.92,0:20:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Chairman's orders! Fall back!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:31.63,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\alpha&HFF&\blur10\fad(0,300)}I say again, the chairman is ordering us {\1a&H00&\3a&H50&}to fall back!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.63,0:20:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I say again, the chairman is ordering us to fall back!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't think this is over.
Comment: 10,0:20:34.63,0:20:36.47,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[Background line 1]
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you rue the day you decided to defy me!
Comment: 10,0:20:36.47,0:20:38.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\an8}[Background line 2]
Dialogue: 9,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}Hostile forces are retreating.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:40.55,0:20:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hostile forces are retreating.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}L-Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.93,0:20:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Looks like it's over.
Dialogue: 9,0:20:47.27,0:20:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}Man, I've never heard anyone say\n"I'll make you rue the day" in real life!
Dialogue: 9,0:20:48.44,0:20:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(300,300)}Man, I've never heard anyone say\n"I'll make you rue the day" in real life!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.27,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I've never heard anyone say\n"I'll make you rue the day" in real life!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:52.73,0:20:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Great work, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.23,0:20:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a very difficult situation.\nGood job{! media} getting through it.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:00.53,0:21:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You girls, too.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}You really saved us there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:01.78,0:21:03.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You really saved us there.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}Thank you, truly.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, truly.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10}Th-That was hardly worth thanking us for.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:05.16,0:21:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That was hardly worth thanking us for.
Dialogue: 9,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\bord4\shad0\c&H000000&\3a&H50&\blur10\fad(0,300)}All in a day's work for first-class outlaws.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.08,0:21:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,All in a day's work for first-class outlaws.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it was, with how fired up you were!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.96,0:21:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell them that!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.71,0:21:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for the next part.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.05,0:21:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We're coming for you,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:24.47,0:21:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hoshino{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.44,0:21:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you attack Abydos?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:35.19,0:21:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid I don't know what you're talking about.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:37.86,0:21:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe you may have gotten a little confused.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:40.74,0:21:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,As promised, I will pay for\nthe majority of the school's debt.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:45.16,0:21:49.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the extent of our agreement, right?
Dialogue: 10,0:21:51.29,0:21:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But that hardly matters.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:53.04,0:21:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you have dropped out,\nthe student council no longer has any members.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:58.51,0:22:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It could hardly be considered a school at this point.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:02.43,0:22:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This whole situation with Abydos\nis merely a preamble to the real event.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:08.06,0:22:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{*}Miss Hoshino{*Hoshino-san}.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:09.43,0:22:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Our eyes were on you from the very beginning.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.77,0:22:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It was paramount you signed that contract\nand surrendered all your rights to us.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.15,0:22:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,To that end, we cooperated with the Kaiser Corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.91,0:22:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,They were merely pawns.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:30.25,0:22:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise if you misunderstood my position,
Dialogue: 10,0:22:33.04,0:22:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was never employed at that paltry corporation.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:39.00,0:22:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've attained the strongest Mystic in Kivotos.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.22,0:22:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't possibly waste that\non mere mercenary work, now could I?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:51.98,0:22:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This fascinating experiment\nis what we've yearned to witness.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope that clears up our intentions.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So that's how it is.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:04.95,0:23:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yet again,
Dialogue: 10,0:23:06.45,0:23:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've been tricked by an adult.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:09.74,0:23:11.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm sorry, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:11.95,0:23:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's all my fault.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:15.62,0:23:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Shiroko{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.00,0:23:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Nonomi{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:18.34,0:23:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Serika{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.63,0:23:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ayane{**-chan}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:20.88,0:23:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}{*}Teacher{*Sensei}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:23.13,0:23:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yume{**-senpai}.
Dialogue: 10,0:23:25.01,0:23:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{=3}{\i1}I'm sorry.

